{{Top|leg}}
A '''fine-point laser cutter''' was a tool used for precise cutting work. [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] used one while repairing his [[Cybernetics/Legends|prosthetic]] [[Limb/Legends|limbs]] in the [[Time/Legends|early]] [[Standard day/Legends|days]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

{{Tech-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
It is possible that this is merely another name for the [[laser scalpel]].

